Autenticação / Usuários (sem auth)
  # Criar usuário
  curl -X POST http://localhost/api/v1/users \
    -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -H "Accept: application/json" \
    -d '{"name":"Teste","email":"teste@email.com","password":"password"}'

  Rotas autenticadas (substitua SEU_TOKEN pelo token do Sanctum)

  # Usuário autenticado
  curl -X GET http://localhost/api/v1/user \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN" \
    -H "Accept: application/json"

  # Usuários
  curl -X GET http://localhost/api/v1/users \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN" \
    -H "Accept: application/json"

  # Status Civil
  curl -X GET http://localhost/api/v1/marital-statuses \
    -H "Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN" \
    -H "Accept: application/json"

